text: Khulwa okhufura khwabu khushialo, nende okhukhola ebifwanga ebibii ne ebifwanga ebibii shibikalushilanga halali khu ulia wabikhola. Ne shibalindanga tawe halali omulukha kwa balia abaranjilila khale, ne sholanyoola abukabukhani khumilukha chia Nyasaye tawe, nohomba sholanyoola abukalukhasio khumilukha chia Nyasaye tawe
